{"tid":271382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"部分慶回歸活動與政府指引不符","createTime":"2017-06-05T04:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T06:41:14.000Z","uid":75927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c768f0065e7b0c73252c35a1ba2c003425022e0b","tid":271382,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=223635&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223635%26refer%3Dshare&d=xp3lZiKZAHy2tdDJ6o9md0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9f07953f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223635%26refer%3Dshare&h=62ff950c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=223635&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今年被列為其中一個慶祝回歸活動，但場地並無任何與慶回歸相關或廿周年的標誌。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慶回歸活動還包括一個保良局幼稚園的水運會。為了與回歸拉上關係，主辦團體有特別安排，舉行回歸盃，邀請其他的學校一起參加。</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a0600733a94216d3d6a10e655198c869d34183c","tid":271382,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c92967706a58023a2818f81c768cdd637f45c4b7","tid":271382,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"保梁局"},{"pid":"c43f590aef27a3be8a6e24011a2a3cdc72e95e56","tid":271382,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3d956bce89204aaf80df94336fa175e79a39409","tid":271382,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"幼稚園都有水運會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533744d426621ffcedbbe939599e8